Package: tula
Type: Package
Title: Stata-Style Regression Output for R Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "email@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tula(), which prints regression output formatted to
    resemble Stata's regression output. Includes a two-block header with
    model fit statistics, a coefficient table with factor variable grouping,
    and an optional confidence interval column. Supports lm() and glm()
    with an extensible S3 dispatch architecture for future model types.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
